<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><lyrics>[V1]
 1. Chi pha chuh tuh unla, zingkal khawvak tung apat in,
 Chi pha chuh tuh unla, sun nisat laiin;
 Chi pha chuh tuh unla, mi lunggil sukipak zelin,
 Chi pha chuh tuh unla, pha takin veng un.

[V2]
 Chi pha chuh tuh unla, Chi pha chuh tuh unla,
 Gunchuh taka lungsiet khuta thehzak zelin;
 Hinna changthak phelsuoh un,
 Chanchin Pha tangko pih un,
 Chi pha chuh tuh unla, khawvel gam tinah.

[V3]
 2. Chi pha chuh tuh unla, zingkal nisuoh tung apat in,
 Chi pha chuh tuh unla, nitum nung inle;
 Chi pha chuh tuh unla, ginglah lo leh lungawi takin,
 Bang cheng Pathiena nga'n, Amah mai gingin.

[V4]
 3. Chi pha chuh tuh unla, kipumpiek na diktak neiin,
 Chi pha chuh tuh unla, sana buh chi chu;
 Chi pha chuh tuh unla, kichawl a mawkum mai lo in,
 Nisa leh guohtui pie di'n Pathien ngen un.</lyrics>
<title>SOWING THE PRECIOUS SEED</title>
<author>(Home Mission Song)</author>
<hymn_number>290</hymn_number>
</song>